title: Good omens animation/Do I wana know
author: Pinkpiggy 93
comment:
Crowley: *Swaggering down the street, radiating coolness.
Aziraphale: "Hello dear!"
Crowley: O_O (*Sweats profusely, trips and face-plants the ground).
I saw that Neil Gaiman retweeted this on Twitter and enjoyed it. I love this!

Every time I assume I'm done with thinking, "I can't believe I lived long enough to see people creating these grand artworks in honor of Good Omens of all things," I am proven wrong! What a time to be alive! It's sappy as hell, but damn, I wish Terry knew how many artists were contributing to his canon.
this whole vid is gold but the Queen vinyl turning into Aziraphale thooo 👏👏
“Crawling back to you” is such a perfect line for these two good god.
